{"pageProps":{"bookInfo":{"id":"58673eba8b130e7348558ee30564e0a8","name":"marked源码解析","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\source\\marked源码解析","chapterList":[{"id":"b2cfb42149a8734e45edf457627a4b3e","type":"chapter","name":"02语法正则二.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\source\\marked源码解析\\02语法正则二.md","url":"/book/58673eba8b130e7348558ee30564e0a8/b2cfb42149a8734e45edf457627a4b3e"},{"id":"77673491a3513f502cad5f07eb7d7242","type":"chapter","name":"03语法正则三.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\source\\marked源码解析\\03语法正则三.md","url":"/book/58673eba8b130e7348558ee30564e0a8/77673491a3513f502cad5f07eb7d7242"},{"id":"8ac594c5dd0d1dcc922bf59f676eae48","type":"chapter","name":"语法正则.md","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\source\\marked源码解析\\语法正则.md","url":"/book/58673eba8b130e7348558ee30564e0a8/8ac594c5dd0d1dcc922bf59f676eae48"}],"title":"语法正则","type":"book","url":"/book/58673eba8b130e7348558ee30564e0a8","content":"\n    \n    \n      <div class=\"crossnote markdown-preview  \">\n      \n<h1 id=\"语法正则\">语法正则 </h1>\n<p>markdown语法<a href=\"http://markdown.p2hp.com\">参考</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"标题\">标题 </h2>\n<p>标题语法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>在单词或短语的前面添加对应个数的 <strong>#</strong> 即可,在 <strong>#</strong> 后面至少要有一个空格<code>/(#{1,6})(?=\\s|$)/</code></li>\n<li>在单词或短语的前面添加对应标题的HTML标签 例如 &lt;h1&gt; 这种暂时不做处理</li>\n<li>在#或者HTML标题标签前面最多添加3个空格   <code>/ {0,3}/</code></li>\n</ol>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"js\" class=\"language-javascript js\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// /(.*)(?:\\n+|$)匹配末尾或者换行前的任意字符，并且换行只匹配但不记住该匹配项</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> heading <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">^ {0,3}(#{1,6})(?=\\s|$)(.*)(?:\\n+|$)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"水平线\">水平线 </h2>\n<p>要创建水平线，请单独在一行上使用三个或更多的<kbdb>*, -, _,  符号之间可以存在空格或者制表符<br>\n前面最多添加3个空格  <code>/ {0,3}/</code></kbdb></p>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"js\" class=\"language-javascript js\"><code><span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> hr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">^ {0,3}((?:-[\\t ]*){3,}|(?:_[ \\t]*){3,}|(?:\\*[ \\t]*){3,})(?:\\n+|$)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"代码块\">代码块 </h2>\n<p>代码块通常缩进四个空格或一个制表符。当它们在列表中时，将它们缩进八个空格或两个制表符。</p>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"js\" class=\"language-javascript js\"><code><span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> blockCode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">^( {4}[^\\n]+(?:\\n(?: *(?:\\n|$))*)?)+</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"清单\">清单 </h2>\n<p>要创建有序列表，请在订单项中添加数字和句点。数字不必按数字顺序排列，但列表应以数字开头<br>\n要创建无序列表，请在订单项前添加破折号（-），星号（*）或加号（+）。缩进一个或多个项目以创建嵌套列表</p>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"js\" class=\"language-javascript js\"><code><span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> bullet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">(?:[*+-]|\\d{1,9}[.)])</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"围栏代码块\">围栏代码块 </h2>\n<p>可以在代码块之前和之后的行上使用三个刻度线（`）或三个波浪号（~） 创建代码块 <code>/(`{3,}(?=[^`\\n]*(?:\\n|$))|~{3,})/</code><br>\n前面最多添加3个空格  <code>/ {0,3}/</code></p>\n<pre data-role=\"codeBlock\" data-info=\"js\" class=\"language-javascript js\"><code><span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> space <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\"> {0,3}</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span>\n<span class=\"token doc-comment comment\">/**\n * `<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>3,<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> 匹配3个```\n * ?=[^`\\n]* 后面不为换行符和`的任意多个字符\n * (?:\\n|$) 匹配结尾或者换行符\n * ~<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>3,<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>)匹配3个~\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> begin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">(`{3,}(?=[^`\\n]*(?:\\n|$))|~{3,})</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span>\n<span class=\"token doc-comment comment\">/**\n * ([^\\n]*) 匹配单行\n * (?:\\n|$) 匹配空格但是不记录\n * (?:|([\\s\\S]*?)(?:\\n|$))\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> content <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">([^\\n]*)(?:\\n|$)(?:|([\\s\\S]*?)(?:\\n|$))</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span>\n<span class=\"token doc-comment comment\">/**\n *  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>0,3<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> 前面最多添加3个空格\n * \\1 反向引用\n * [~`]* 匹配连续的零个或者多个~`\n *  *(?=\\n|$)| 匹配连续的零个或者多个空格\n * $ 匹配结尾\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> end <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">(?: {0,3}\\1[~`]* *(?=\\n|$)|$)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// fences = /^space begin content end/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword keyword-const\">const</span> fences <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">^ {0,3}(`{3,}(?=[^`\\n]*(?:\\n|$))|~{3,})([^\\n]*)(?:\\n|$)(?:|([\\s\\S]*?)(?:\\n|$))(?: {0,3}\\1[~`]* *(?=\\n|$)|$)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md-sidebar-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc\">\n<details style=\"padding:0;;padding-left:0px;\" open=\"\">\n        <summary class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\">\n          <a href=\"#语法正则\" class=\"md-toc-link\"><p>语法正则</p>\n</a>\n          </summary>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#标题\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>标题</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#水平线\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>水平线</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#代码块\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>代码块</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#清单\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>清单</p>\n\n          </a></div><div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:42px\">\n          <a href=\"#围栏代码块\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>围栏代码块</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n      <a id=\"sidebar-toc-btn\">≡</a>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n<script>\n\nvar sidebarTOCBtn = document.getElementById('sidebar-toc-btn')\nsidebarTOCBtn.addEventListener('click', function(event) {\n  event.stopPropagation()\n  if (document.body.hasAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')) {\n    document.body.removeAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')\n  } else {\n    document.body.setAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc', true)\n  }\n})\n</script>\n      \n  \n    <script>\n</script>"},"revalidate":200,"title":"语法正则"},"__N_SSG":true}